11:14–15</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/crucifixion?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Crucifixion</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note10a\" data-full-marker=\"10a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847215\" id=\"note10a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/matt/27.24-25?lang=fra#p24\">Mt 27:24–25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"11\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note11a\" data-full-marker=\"11a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847219\" id=\"note11a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.11-12?lang=fra#p11\">1 Né 22:11–12</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.2?lang=fra#p2\">2 Né 9:2</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note11b\" data-full-marker=\"11b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847223\" id=\"note11b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/hosea/3.5?lang=fra#p5\">Os 3:5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note11c\" data-full-marker=\"11c\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847228\" id=\"note11c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/israel?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Israël — Rassemblement d’Israël</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847232\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1-2?lang=fra#p1\">1 Né 14:1–2</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.9-10?lang=fra#p9\">2 Né 10:9–10</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note12b\" data-full-marker=\"12b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117847235\" id=\"note12b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/devil?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Diable — Église du diable</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note12c\" data-full-mar